commit.message:
fix bug in documentation

When multiple_tables=True, pd.DataFrame() is used
When multiple_tables=False, pd.read_csv() is used
Above is what I found to be true when using tabula-py

The documentation has the contradicting statements about this. This commit corrects the wrong statement.
